    • connectChild

      public boolean connectChild(TwoThreeFourTreeNode childNode)
      Method used to connect a child node to the node. Works if the node is type 0,1,2 but not if 3, or if a child node is in the location that it is supposed to go in. For precondition, we will need to check that the location that the child node is going to go into is empty
      Parameters:
      childNode - being added
      Returns:
      true upon successful implementation
